                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Discussed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7091&quot; title=&quot;support custom GC options in hbase-env.sh&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-7091&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-7091&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br/&gt;
It&apos;s not critical, but a little bit surprising, as the comments in bin/hbase doesn&apos;t say anything about this. If you create your own hbase-env then it&apos;s not an issue...&lt;/p&gt;</description>
